        <footnote id="F5">On January 12, 2018, the recipient was granted 12,379 options.  4,126 stock options are fully vested and currently exercisable, 4,126 stock options will vest on January 12, 2020 and 4,127 stock options will vest on January 12, 2021.</footnote>
